{"tid":934712,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我要有鼻敏感dllm","createTime":"2018-12-09T13:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T13:18:34.000Z","uid":211480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac0ede2521ecad55fe94ca3466ca3c2012dedce","tid":934712,"uid":211480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:14:38.000Z","msg":"近排轉天氣真係好似攞左我條命<br />\n朝早一起身「呻」番一包半包紙巾簡直係例行公事<br />\n一個唔好彩 個日你就係咁先<br />\n因為個日你冇帶番十包八包紙巾出街都搞唔掂 鼻水流嘅速度同量永遠都超過你可以想像<br />\n好辛苦呀dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打住咁多先 出番去「呻」鼻涕先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fedf174ba76611521dade0758befb7eabedcaf9b","tid":934712,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"由細到大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab5e4f9ef7da2a260b6268c032d6a86d28e3279","tid":934712,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:15:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96b588087fc89c29e887bb1e63cdf822cb6706a0","tid":934712,"uid":211480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dab5e4f9ef7da2a260b6268c032d6a86d28e3279","tid":934712,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:15:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:18:34.000Z","msg":"dnlm"}]}